# Propel hourly ingestion (V1 scheduler).
#
# cron runs with an empty environment, so the container entrypoint snapshots the
# process environment to /etc/propel-ingestion.env at startup and the wrapper
# sources it. Output is sent to PID 1's stdout/stderr so it shows up in
# `docker logs` (and, in prod, wherever the task's stdout is collected).
SHELL=/bin/sh
0 * * * * root /usr/local/bin/propel-ingestion > /proc/1/fd/1 2> /proc/1/fd/2
